================================================================================
What this package contains
================================================================================

This package is a Swift binding to sudachi.rs and does NOT redistribute any
SudachiDict dictionary data. The compiled binary (Sudachi.xcframework)
statically links:

  sudachi.rs — https://github.com/WorksApplications/sudachi.rs
  Copyright (c) Works Applications Co., Ltd.
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The default runtime configuration embedded in the binary
(crates/sudachi-swift-uniffi/src/default_config.json) is derived from
third_party/sudachi.rs/resources/sudachi.json (Apache-2.0). The auxiliary
resource files char.def and unk.def used at runtime also originate from
sudachi.rs (Apache-2.0).

Bindings are generated with Mozilla UniFFI (https://github.com/mozilla/uniffi-rs,
Mozilla Public License 2.0), which is a build-time tool and is not linked into
the distributed binary.

